content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Multiple process image file exclusion lists January 31, 2025—In Server & Workload Protection, the process image file list is now part of the inheritance exclusion list, and applies to real-time exclusions. The setting is available through Server & Workload Protection > Policies > Anti-Malware > Exclusions. For more information, see Overview section of the policy editor.
